entries.message: // Momentum   if (progress >= 0.8) {     insight += "It’s nearing completion. 🚀 ";   } else if (progress >= 0.5) {     insight += "Steady momentum—about halfway through. 📈 ";   } else if (progress > 0) {     insight += "It’s just getting off the ground. ✍ ";   } else if (status === 'Planned') {     insight += "Still on the launchpad. 🧪 ";   }
